Perfect — now we know the exact issue.

Your package.json file is broken because the JSON formatting is invalid.

This line from the log tells us that:

SyntaxError: /vercel/path0/package.json: Expected ',' or '}' after property value in JSON

So Vercel cannot even read package.json.

Easiest fix

You need to replace your whole package.json with a clean version.

Do this exactly in GitHub
Step 1

Open your GitHub repo

Step 2

Click on:

package.json
Step 3

Click the pencil/edit button

Step 4

Delete everything in that file

Step 5

Paste this exact version:

{
  "name": "propcon-canvassing-app",
  "private": true,
  "version": "1.0.0",
